{"tid":334203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(港人迷思)到底香港係多善良既人定on9","createTime":"2017-07-24T13:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T13:44:24.000Z","uid":130894,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9c677280a7dfd61c0634ff6577c177f00016e0","tid":334203,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T13:32:17.000Z","msg":"話說我朋友早兩個月係旺角俾人呃左3千蚊<br />\n<br />\n事源係咁的。<br />\n<br />\n有個女人同我朋友講話係外國番黎，銀行食左卡，無錢住酒店，可以俾條鏈做抵押，問我朋友借幾千，第二日俾番我朋友，咁我朋友就唔要俾條鏈咁借俾佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n最後當然無左影。<br />\n<br />\n朋友即日同我講果陣我都已經覺得好多疑點，話佢on9。姐係酒店唔係應該一早book定既，就算唔係，而家你無得揀，賓館都要住啦，點解要借咁多。其次我自己都好多時遇到人R錢，例如話無錢食飯，咁如果我唔趕我都會直接帶佢去食野埋單，唔會俾現金。<br />\n然後我朋友今日send左條link俾我(如下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%A5%B3%E8%80%81%E5%8D%83%E5%80%9F%E6%95%91%E5%91%BD%E9%8C%A2-3%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%A4%B1%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-133507109.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2580%259F%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%2591%25BD%25E9%258C%25A2-3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E9%2580%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-133507109.html&d=786xU7PnK6mKZu4gmYOL3TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e175b286\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%A5%B3%E8%80%81%E5%8D%83%E5%80%9F%E6%95%91%E5%91%BD%E9%8C%A2-3%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%A4%B1%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-133507109.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/212759_faf5cad792c3b586810ff6b516438b62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F212759_faf5cad792c3b586810ff6b516438b62.jpg&h=4a9f0c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後令我反思既唔係d人有幾蠢，最近見好多post話外國人好，香港人冷感無情。<br />\n而我見到條新聞會諗，到底其實香港都真係有咁多好人，定其實香港人係on9，咁好呃呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人好nice<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多on9無判斷力抵死"},{"pid":"dd6bebdf976664dda4fe50a27d8c5c466d38bd65","tid":334203,"uid":94009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"同中國接軌 以後冇人敢係街扶人起身 冇人敢借錢 撞車車到人一定要補一下車死佢為止<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中華民族萬歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}